content: That's a great idea about incorporating a short exercise routine into my morning routine. I think I'll start with some light stretching and yoga to get my blood flowing and energy levels up. I'm also considering adding a quick 10-minute walk outside to get some fresh air and sunlight. Do you think it's a good idea to prioritize my most important tasks during my extra hour on Wednesdays, Thursdays, and Fridays, or should I use that time to focus on my side project?
